quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  11,6,"Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, mebla ma illa ôôeéq is ar Öebbi. Issen tanezdu$t is, tanîelt is. Meôôa, di Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  11,7,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Asgeld iS illa $ef waman. A kwen Ijeôôeb anwi segwen ara ixedmen ayen ilhan, sennig wiyav. Ma tenniv: \"ih, kunwi a d tekkrem deffir tmeppant nnwen\", wid ijehlen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"ayagi, kan, d ssêur n ûûeê"
  11,8,"Ma Neswexxeô asen aâaqeb ar imir ipwassnen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"d acu iT iîîfen\"? Ass ideg ara ten id iawev, day illa wa ara ten iveôôfen segs? Ad asen izzi wayen i$ef pmmaâliken"
  11,9,"Ma Nesêess i umdan aêunu nne¨£, sinna, Nekkes as t, atan ad iayes, ad ijhel"
  11,10,"Ma Nesêess as l$it, deffir twa$it i t innulen, atan ad yini: \"fukkent felli lemêayen\", d$a, neppa, ad ifôeê, ad izux"
  11,11,"Kkes ed wid iûebbôen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I widak ssmaê akked tikci meqqwôen"
  11,12,"Ahat teppaoav kra n wayen ik ed ippuweêêan. Pzemmiven yis idmaren ik mara qqaôen: \"a lemmer i s d irs ugerruj, ne$ idda d, yides, lmelk\"! Keçç d aneddaô kan. Öebbi d Awkil n yal cci"
  11,13,"Ne$ ad inin: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"awit ed, s usnulfu, mraw n tsuôtin am neppa. Naâôet ayen iwumi tzemrem, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  11,14,"Ma ur awen d rran ara, cfut ar irs ed kan s tussna n Öebbi, ar ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, ma kunwi d imvuâen"
  11,15,"I wid ib$an tameddurt n ddunit akked ôôêuê is, a Nkafi, degs, igiten nnsen, ur asen Ntekkes"
  11,16,"Widak, ur ppafen, di laxeôt, siwa times. Ad i$li wayen ûenâen degs; inqev wayen xeddmen"
  11,17,"Day win iddan d ubeggen, s$uô Mass is, u immal as t unagi s$uôeS…? U, uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Wigi umnen yis. Win i p inekôen, seg ikubar, ppaâud is d times. Ur ppili di ccekk fellas. Neppa, ih, d tidep s$uô Mass ik. Maca, tegwti n medden ur ppamnen"
  11,18,"Anwa idensen sennig win id isnulfan tikerkas $ef Öebbi? Wigi a d rsen i Mass nnsen. A d inin inagan: \"d wigi i iskaddben $ef Mass nnsen\". Day Öebbi ur Ixezzu yara imednas"
  11,19,"I isîixxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, i t issarmen d uâwij, nitni ur uminen s laxeôt"
  11,20,"Wigi, ur sfunnugen di tmurt, ur asen illi bab, war Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb ar wayev. Ur zmiren ad slen, ur pwalin"
  11,21,D wigi i isxesôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen
  11,22,"Ur illi ccekk, ih, nitni ad xesôen, di laxeôt, sennig wiyav"
  11,23,"Ih, wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, u unzen aS i Mass nnsen, widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen"